    <h1>Homepage</h1> <br>

    <h3>Quick Guide</h3>
    <img src="/public/images/welcome.gif" alt="Welcome .gif" />
    <p><strong>This bot only works on groups.</strong></p>
    <ol>
        <li>Add your
            <strong>Exaroton API key</strong> and
            <strong>your server ID</strong>
            (you can get it <a href="#">here</a>, and add it <a href="#">here</a>).
        </li>
        <li>Add the bot to the group.</li>
        <li>Go to the <a href="#">groups page</a> and authorize the group.</li>
        <li>Add authorized numbers (include country code, e.g., <code>+62...</code>) on <a href="#">this page</a>.</li>
        <li>You and your friends (the authorized ones) can fiddle with the server through the group ðŸ˜„ Enjoy gaming!
        </li>
    </ol>

    <h3>Basic Commands</h3>
    @ the bot to get started, then use follow it with these:
    <p>

    <ul>
        <li> <code>/help</code> shows the manual page/guide thru WhatsApp chat for commands available</li>
        <li> <code>/servers</code> shows available server ids</li>
        <li> <code>/start [server-id]</code> starts the server specified by its id</li>
        <li> <code>/stop [server-id]</code> stops the server specified by its id</li>
        <li> <code>/info [server-id]</code> shows the current server info</li>
        <li> <code>/players [server-id]</code> shows the players that are currently online on a server</li>
    </ul>

    <br> <br>
</main>

